inspired by a viewing of les allumettes animées [ animated matches ] ( 1908 ) by émile cohl , starewicz decided to re - create the fight through stop - motion animation : by replacing the beetles ' legs with wire , attached with sealing wax to their thorax , he is able to create articulated insect puppets .

world of animation : like george pal 's " toons " , director ladislas starevich was best known for animation using these 3-d figures

